chat:g-agent-main-cron-3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1775078029574,"sessionId":"622d1d1e-402e-4b25-b9d8-cef929e9227b","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":48800,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/622d1d1e-402e-4b25-b9d8-cef929e9227b.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check for active sessions first."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_uls3tjhc8ju5_1","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"activeMinutes":5,"messageLimit":1}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775078030059}]}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775078032963}}
{"type":"message","id":"c53603e6","parentId":"30dd202a","timestamp":"2026-04-01T21:13:57.796Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The only session is the current cron session itself - it's a system session, not a user conversation. The last message is from the assistant (me), not from a user. There's no active user conversation happening.\n\nSo I should proceed with the autonomous learning task. Let me search for relevant industry news on enterprise digital transformation, smart security, network system integration, and IT operations services.","thinkingSignature":"b8dd96579d43c7c8ae5aa7c5112db2081c818cd28ce5c7158b4b504f1e06065c"},{"type":"text","text":"检测到当前只有cron系统会话在运行，没有活跃用户对话。执行自主学习任务。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gvfk5af1wh6i_1","name":"sessions_history","arguments":{"sessionKey":"agent:main","limit":2}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gvfk5af1wh6i_2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":809,"output":171,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44961,"cost":{"input":0.0002427,"output":0.0002052,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00176733}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775078032967}}
{"type":"message","id":"ba949930","parentId":"c53603e6","timestamp":"2026-04-01T21:13:57.891Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_gvfk5af1wh6i_1","toolName":"sessions_history","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main\",\n  \"messages\": [],\n  \"truncated\": false,\n  \"droppedMessages\": false,\n  \"contentTruncated\": false,\n  \"contentRedacted\": false,\n  \"bytes\": 2\n}"}],"details":{"sessionKey":"agent:main","messages":[],"truncated":false,"droppedMessages":false,"contentTruncated":false,"contentRedacted":false,"bytes":2},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775078037885}}
{"type":"message","id":"aa2924db","parentId":"ba949930","timestamp":"2026-04-01T21:13:57.897Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_gvfk5af1wh6i_2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775078037894}}
{"type":"message","id":"f46114b5","parentId":"aa2924db","timestamp":"2026-04-01T21:14:03.646Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now I'll search for industry news on enterprise digital transformation, smart security, network system integration, and IT operations services. Let me run multiple searches in parallel.","thinkingSignature":"ee0d3f9b47b96af7eb134f390436220e0f0ca7bd42fda66884cd65b07b4608a1"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_b428p7chk0e1_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026最新政策趋势\" 2>&1","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_b428p7chk0e1_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防行业 2026市场动态技术趋势\" 2>&1","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_b428p7chk0e1_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"IT运维服务 2026行业发展趋势\" 2>&1","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_b428p7chk0e1_4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成 2026政企市场动态\" 2>&1","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1548,"output":249,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45778,"cost":{"input":0.00046439999999999996,"output":0.0002988,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00208263}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775078037897}}
